creator: VINCI Autoroutes
descriptionHtml:
With the Ulys app, your e-toll badge has a multitude of functions.

E-TOLL SUBSCRIBERS, ULYS BY VINCI AUTOROUTES WILL BOOST YOUR BADGE
- Monitor your e-toll expenses and view your invoices in the blink of an eye.
- Manage your plan and access all your options in one click, wherever you are.
- Keep Customer Service at your fingertips and replace your badge or order new mounting brackets in just one click.

THE ULYS BY VINCI AUTOROUTES APP MAKES YOUR LIFE EASIER
- Save time: a high performance GPS keeps you informed of traffic, roadworks and any events on the road in real time.
- Manage your toll budget: toll prices are indicated on your itinerary.
- Travel safely on the motorway: your smartphone transforms into an emergency call terminal in the event of an accident.

THE ULYS BY VINCI AUTOROUTES APP SIMPLIFIES YOUR JOURNEYS
- Depart with peace of mind: we offer advice and tips to prepare for all your journeys.
- Never stop at random again: find details on the service & rest areas on your way before departing and during your journey in real time.

And this is only the beginning!
Your app will continue to improve for you and with you. New mobility services will shortly be available to enrich your experience on the road.


Any concerns or questions?
Please check our FAQs or get in touch with Customer Service team is available to advise you in French, Monday to Saturday, from 8am to 8pm, on 0 970 820 160 (free service + price of call).


Any suggestion to improve the Ulys app? Your feedback is very valuable to us so please don’t hesitate and drop us a line at: suggestion.app@vinci-autoroutes.com

Follow us on social media to stay up-to-date on our latest news:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/UlysByVINCIAutoroutes/

And visit our website: https://ulys.vinci-autoroutes.com/

Together, we will enjoy many excellent journeys

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
With lockdown progressively being lifted, mobility, although limited, is slowly picking up. Ulys helps you by offering real time updates on services available at service areas. The Ulys app tells you everything from which shops are open to where you can find open toilet facilities, or shower facilities for HGV drivers.

Find traffic information for your journey on the VINCI Autoroutes motorway network, both when preparing your trip and whilst driving using the in-app GPS.
